            <thetext>Thanks for the patch! I added the two loader classes and introduced a new Test Runner config macro, TEST_LOADER. By default, only the test-mobile and test-mobile-source jobs set it to &quot;testrunner.TestLoaderMobile&quot;, you can override it in your config.json if you want to build a Test Runner with a mobile application for the tests and a desktop/widget UI.

Fixed with 4f38483b (master)</thetext>
